[[Biblia|Biblia]] Kristanvanchem Povitr Pustok. Taka Povitr Pustok aniek nanv. Haka 2 bhag asat. Adlo korar ani Novo korar. Adlea koraran 46 pustokam, zalear novea koraran 27 pustokam asat. Sogllim mellun 73 pustokam Bible-ant melltat.[[File:Holy Bible.JPG|thumb|Povitr Pustok]]

Adlea koraran survek [[Pentateuk|Pentateuk]] pustokam, magir itihasachim pustokam, zannvaiechim ani provadianchim pustokam asat. Novea koraran [[Xubhvortoman|Xubhvortoman]] vo [[Vanjel|Vanjel]], [[Dhormdutancho Itihas|Dhormdutancho Itihas]], [[Chitti|chitti]] ani [[Prokasovnni|Prokasovnni]]chim pustokam melltam.

